{"tid":1565804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 回應831太子站有假消防謬論","createTime":"2019-09-13T09:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T01:07:04.000Z","uid":39808,"like":27,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff59935a9c613c0620d66d2f25409a346b09adf","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:46:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">先講結論，有人故意挑撥抗爭者同消防，更嚴重嘅係話有假消防嘅存在，促使抗爭者與消防間的不信任，如果惡化下去，有人會阻礙消防乃至救護工作，係對應人群如紅海嘅反擊。<br />\n<br />\n呢招其實係鼓吹有鬼嘅延伸，因為唔喺內部亂咁捉鬼已經係抗爭者嘅共識，所以現在對家就鼓吹外部捉鬼，連登仔信撚咗仲要係咁推，更加幫埋手穿鑿附會，對家又得分啦。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據如下<br />\nUFC南亞仔 (#161430) 開咗個post<br />\n[真相再浮現?] 消防同證人可能都冇講大話！但有神秘假消防抬走嘔白泡傷者！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563130</a><br />\n<br />\n首先，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">UFC南亞仔 (#161430) 並唔係 UST南亞仔</span>。<br />\n入正題，個post spin 話有假消防，然後我打緊呢個post時，已有2500個正皮。<br />\n<br />\nUFC南亞仔咁講，但當中滲有流料，有意誤導<br />\n（▽▽▽截圖▽▽▽）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXSWYMb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXSWYMb.png&h=f7142bbd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（△△△截圖△△△）<br />\n流料：今日消防又咁回應: 2. 消防11:30先進入到太子站內<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">UFC南亞仔話有假消防嘅推論係立足於流料上</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">我係有喺佢個post先後兩次直接問佢有關講法嘅來源，但佢無回應，至於來源以外嘅其他言論倒是有回應。畀哂機會UFC南亞仔澄清㗎啦。</span><br />\n<br />\n而事實上，當日消防在記者會上講嘅，同UFC南亞仔講嘅，係唔同，消防記者會大家可以翻睇去查證，所以我可以斷言UFC南亞仔係老屈消防。<br />\n<blockquote>今日（9月12日）下午2時半，消防處召開記者會解釋831太子站救援過程，由副救護總長曾敏霞及副消防總長（總部）陳慶勇代表回應。陳慶勇先指出，昨日由立法會議員毛孟靜公開的紀錄文件為消防內部文件，當中有消防的慣用術語，可能會有錯誤解讀或引起誤會，但他承認該紀錄文件與當日完整的行動紀錄吻合。<br />\n<br />\n記者會開始之初，陳慶勇先向傳媒講述當日收到救援求助的情況：<br />\n<br />\n    第一宗事故為當晚的10時49分，消防接報指有市民從直播中看到有長者在太子站內被打傷，而救護員到場時間為11時31分，但當時太子站已封站。<br />\n<br />\n    第二宗事故為10時56分，消防接報指太子站內有3名人士被打傷，救護員到場時間為11時17分，3分鐘後已由E出入口進入站內救援。陳慶勇強調此次並非處理大型傷者事件。至11時24分，站內有一名女士報稱受驚，救護員轉為安慰該名女士，後11時31分簽署不需要送院文件後離開太子站。<br />\n<br />\n    第三宗事故發生於10時57分，消防接報太子站發生二級火警。<span style=\"color: gold;\">消防員於11時01分到達現場，11點06分由B1出入口進入太子站，惟及後未發現火警，但於月台見到不少傷者，而因消防隊隊員中有部份人具有先遣急救員資格，後改為照顧港鐵站內的傷者。</span><br />\n<br />\n    第四宗事故發生於11時05分，指太子站3號月台有大量傷者，其後消防確認為「特別服務－涉及大量傷者事故」。救護車與指揮官11時14分到場，但因港鐵站已封站，後於與警方協調後，<span style=\"color: gold;\">在晚上11時31分容許<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一名「見習救護主任」</span>經B出口進入月台。</span><br />\n<br />\n原文：《831太子站疑雲：消防處稱沒有目擊死亡；傷者數字前後不一，不排除「數錯」》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20190912-whatsnew-831-prince-edward-station-incident/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20190912-whatsnew-831-prince-edward-station-incident%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=09eb0e15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20190912-whatsnew-831-prince-edward-station-incident/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外，有證詞話現場有人失去意識後醒返<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iM51978.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiM51978.png&h=1df9a493&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根據龍小姐所講，佢口中被4名消防員抬走嘅男子，有可能被送往瑪嘉烈醫院 (見第三段)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQwT1gN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQwT1gN.png&h=93b185c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n補充，消防嘅講法其實由9月10日到9月12日記者會都無出現過UFC南亞仔所講嘅流料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94fEWSb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94fEWSb.png&h=08cabb8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6gkGiS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6gkGiS.png&h=80ef97ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後，連登仔女，用下個腦啦屌，唔係就同班藍絲、廢老一撚樣咁智障。</span><br />\n個流料老屈post正負皮數 2552：12（今日某個時間點，唔查最新數字啦），反映有好撚多係跟風同無查證無思考過。好多口口聲聲fact check，大部分都係念口簧同叫人做，得把口就唔撚會做fact check。見到正負皮一面倒就諗都唔使諗去跟風，見到正皮多又唔使諗鳩推。<br />\n<br />\n（之前開咗另一個帖，現在轉標題加補充再開）"},{"pid":"b15b0661be75c801373617f475fcbffcd2f56cf3","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1a70671269a71fd73267d426f19cc8abef75b7f1","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:56:20.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e846292c0a5dadd60d6c4692b1756e3992358ff4","tid":1565804,"uid":199907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:58:02.000Z","msg":"推,我都明明聽到話11：01到左點解仲有人話有假消防"},{"pid":"b20ddf76a00a36a9be5805536fb96ac523b46b27","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:58:06.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"08eec05fae68ccb8d685430c7e170f3600241da3","tid":1565804,"uid":59961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:58:40.000Z","msg":"但係消防講大話話冇見過昏迷傷者"},{"pid":"398b26aaeb8b62b93c01ad7d2d3d7023cd3e5ff5","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:58:45.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"3944ba7272d0ca46446b924a6726b927e150c537","tid":1565804,"uid":71635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:59:29.000Z","msg":"總之太子站同新屋嶺係有人死"},{"pid":"ddcc68c7a1861c286dd413454c32bd60c9ff877d","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08eec05fae68ccb8d685430c7e170f3600241da3","tid":1565804,"uid":59961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:58:40.000Z","msg":"但係消防講大話話冇見過昏迷傷者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:06:04.000Z","msg":"個月台咁長，見唔到唔係無可能<br />\n<br />\n反而想知呢個去咗邊<br />\n23:00 義務急救員在太子站<span style=\"color: orange;\">找到一名暈倒女子</span>，並目睹速龍小隊及防暴警察在月台揮動警棍、拘捕部份人<br />\n來源 義務急救員Kelly from 紅媒01報導"},{"pid":"64c9c345055e7cd42251e135d4c0d89c203957cb","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:06:57.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"447ff84e0e99d843e6e72e5c02ee34b08dbee644","tid":1565804,"uid":299467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b764e5bbfc29519a66292ea95142c8c667785c4","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a3ca5458545da37efa7ae08dcfaa757e209d92e9","tid":1565804,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:09:42.000Z","msg":"黑色五毛警告<br />\n<br />\n黑色分化警告<br />\n<br />\n黑色fake news警告<br />\n<br />\n大家用腦，完"},{"pid":"2a3f7fade10912b7133ebbbb1aeddfd87bb6ab5c","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d2d5ef35858301c0e03d4b6562db741ac81bc176","tid":1565804,"uid":321059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"但仲係解釋唔到龍小姐話消防抬走咗嘔白泡男子喎"},{"pid":"59632e8fb5c25dc8412a54cb7ed741bc97b019ea","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"76834a0767f950520e1878b42704d4ec68baf804","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2d5ef35858301c0e03d4b6562db741ac81bc176","tid":1565804,"uid":321059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"但仲係解釋唔到龍小姐話消防抬走咗嘔白泡男子喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:16:32.000Z","msg":"有人話現場有人失去意識後醒返，如果係同一人就好。<br />\n唔排除有其他可能"},{"pid":"2cd85c8cde5a4c9b149164fc87f6882bfcbdb16c","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:18:41.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7e2da78d75208c1d3054d2eef0be670baa187af5","tid":1565804,"uid":321059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76834a0767f950520e1878b42704d4ec68baf804","tid":1565804,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d